{"chapters": {"parte01-a-transformacao-e-o-trabalho": ["<div class=\"slide cover\"><div class=\"wordmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span><span class=\"name\">Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"kicker\">DIE VERWANDLUNG (1915)</div><h1><span class=\"lt\">A</span> <span class=\"bd\">METAMORFOSE</span></h1><div class=\"author\">por Franz Kafka</div><div class=\"hook\"><span class=\"num\">4</span><span class=\"lbl\">ideias<br>que <span>ficam</span></span></div><div class=\"swipe\"><span>arrasta</span><span class=\"arrow\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M12 32h36M34 18l16 14-16 14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept warn\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">01</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>01</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">O Absurdo Sem Explicação</div><div class=\"card-body\">A metamorfose é dada na primeira frase — sem causa, diagnóstico ou tentativa de cura. O leitor (e o próprio Gregor) trata o impossível como <strong>problema logístico</strong>: o trem perdido, o chefe à porta.</div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 8l20 8v13c0 14-9 23-20 27-11-4-20-13-20-27V16z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Como aplicar:</strong> note quando um sistema absorve o absurdo como rotina — esse é o efeito kafkiano.</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">02</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>02</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 10L54 22 32 34 10 22 32 10z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M10 32l22 12 22-12M10 42l22 12 22-12\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">O Provedor-Máquina</div><div class=\"card-body\">Gregor sustenta pai, mãe e irmã e vive em função do dever, não de si. O emprego de caixeiro-viajante é um cárcere: viagens sem fim, contatos passageiros, medo do patrão. <strong>Sua identidade está soldada ao papel de provedor.</strong></div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Para refletir:</strong> sem a função, o lugar dele na família evapora.</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">03</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>03</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M6 32s10-16 26-16 26 16 26 16-10 16-26 16S6 32 6 32z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"32\" r=\"7\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">A Engrenagem Burocrática</div><div class=\"card-body\">Ao primeiro atraso, o gerente da firma aparece <em>em pessoa</em> — a suspeita corporativa é instantânea. O indivíduo é sempre menor que o sistema impessoal que o cerca.</div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Modelo mental:</strong> o gerente é a voz do sistema; foge horrorizado e sela a perda do emprego.</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">04</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>04</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M10 32h16M38 32h16\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><path d=\"M22 24l-6 8 6 8M42 24l6 8-6 8\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">A Porta e a Primeira Ferida</div><div class=\"card-body\">Gregor abre a porta com as mandíbulas e se mostra; o pânico é geral. O pai o empurra de volta ao quarto com bengala e jornal, <strong>ferindo-o no vão da porta</strong> — primeira ferida de uma série. A porta vira a medida da exclusão.</div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Símbolo:</strong> a porta é a fronteira entre o humano (a sala) e o exilado (o quarto).</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide cta\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"bottom:150px;right:40px;font-size:300px\">+</div><div class=\"big\">Gostou?<br><span class=\"lt\">tem mais.</span></div><div class=\"rows\"><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M14 12h36v40H14z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M14 24h36M14 38h36M24 12v12M40 24v14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>O livro inteiro em 1 página: cheat sheet + PDF no <strong>acervo</strong> &mdash; link na bio.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"32\" r=\"22\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><path d=\"M27 23l16 9-16 9z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Prefere assistir? Resumo de ~5 min no <strong>YouTube</strong>.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Um grande livro destilado por semana. <strong>Siga @minutoreal1701</strong>.</p></div></div><div class=\"save\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M18 10h28v44L32 44 18 54z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>Salve para revisar</div><div class=\"handle\">@minutoreal1701</div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i></div></div>"], "parte02-adaptacao-e-a-maca": ["<div class=\"slide cover\"><div class=\"wordmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span><span class=\"name\">Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"kicker\">DIE VERWANDLUNG (1915)</div><h1><span class=\"lt\">A</span> <span class=\"bd\">METAMORFOSE</span></h1><div class=\"author\">por Franz Kafka</div><div class=\"hook\"><span class=\"num\">4</span><span class=\"lbl\">ideias<br>que <span>ficam</span></span></div><div class=\"swipe\"><span>arrasta</span><span class=\"arrow\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M12 32h36M34 18l16 14-16 14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">01</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>01</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"20\" r=\"10\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><path d=\"M14 52c0-10 8-18 18-18s18 8 18 18\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">Corpo × Humanidade</div><div class=\"card-body\">Gregor adquire hábitos de bicho (rasteja pelas paredes, prefere comida estragada), mas conserva memória, afeto e vergonha. <strong>Por dentro, segue humano; por fora, é repugnante.</strong> A consciência resiste enquanto o corpo a trai.</div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Para refletir:</strong> o que define o humano — a aparência que os outros veem ou a consciência que ninguém alcança?</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">02</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>02</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 10v40M18 50h28\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><path d=\"M14 20h36\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><path d=\"M14 20l-6 12a7 7 0 0 0 12 0L14 20zM50 20l-6 12a7 7 0 0 0 12 0L50 20z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">A Inversão Começa</div><div class=\"card-body\">Cada membro da família reassume uma função produtiva. O pai renasce como autoridade fardada e vigorosa; a mãe costura; Grete cuida do quarto. <strong>Gregor, antes o eixo, vira peso morto.</strong></div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Modelo mental:</strong> a energia vital é uma só e migra — da família para Gregor (antes), de Gregor para a família (agora).</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept warn\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">03</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>03</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M14 14h36v18c0 12-9 22-18 22s-18-10-18-22z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><circle cx=\"24\" cy=\"28\" r=\"3\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><circle cx=\"40\" cy=\"28\" r=\"3\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><path d=\"M26 40a8 6 0 0 0 12 0\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">Os Móveis e o Retrato</div><div class=\"card-body\">Mãe e Grete tentam esvaziar o quarto para Gregor rastejar — sem ver que arrancam dele os <strong>últimos vestígios do humano</strong>. Ele se lança sobre o retrato da dama de peles e o cobre com o corpo: não deixará que o levem.</div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 8l20 8v13c0 14-9 23-20 27-11-4-20-13-20-27V16z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Símbolo:</strong> esvaziar o quarto = transformá-lo em jaula nua, apagar o homem que Gregor foi.</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">04</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>04</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">A Maçã Encravada</div><div class=\"card-body\">O pai chega do trabalho, interpreta a cena como ataque e bombardeia Gregor com maçãs. Uma se crava nas costas com tal força que <strong>ali permanece, apodrecendo na carne</strong> — a ferida que nunca cicatriza e inicia o declínio.</div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Leitura:</strong> a maçã = violência paterna petrificada + punição edípica + eco da maçã bíblica (pecado e queda).</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide cta\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"bottom:150px;right:40px;font-size:300px\">+</div><div class=\"big\">Gostou?<br><span class=\"lt\">tem mais.</span></div><div class=\"rows\"><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M14 12h36v40H14z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M14 24h36M14 38h36M24 12v12M40 24v14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>O livro inteiro em 1 página: cheat sheet + PDF no <strong>acervo</strong> &mdash; link na bio.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"32\" r=\"22\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><path d=\"M27 23l16 9-16 9z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Prefere assistir? Resumo de ~5 min no <strong>YouTube</strong>.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Um grande livro destilado por semana. <strong>Siga @minutoreal1701</strong>.</p></div></div><div class=\"save\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M18 10h28v44L32 44 18 54z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>Salve para revisar</div><div class=\"handle\">@minutoreal1701</div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i></div></div>"], "parte03-declinio-morte-e-renascimento": ["<div class=\"slide cover\"><div class=\"wordmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span><span class=\"name\">Minuto<b>Real</b></span></div><div class=\"kicker\">DIE VERWANDLUNG (1915)</div><h1><span class=\"lt\">A</span> <span class=\"bd\">METAMORFOSE</span></h1><div class=\"author\">por Franz Kafka</div><div class=\"hook\"><span class=\"num\">4</span><span class=\"lbl\">ideias<br>que <span>ficam</span></span></div><div class=\"swipe\"><span>arrasta</span><span class=\"arrow\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M12 32h36M34 18l16 14-16 14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"4\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">01</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>01</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M48 14C28 14 14 28 14 48c20 0 34-14 34-34z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M22 42L42 22\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">A Arte como Último Laço</div><div class=\"card-body\">Ao ouvir Grete tocar violino, Gregor é tomado de emoção e se arrasta para a sala, fascinado, sentindo que a música o chama de volta ao humano. <strong>A alma resiste no corpo de bicho</strong> — e é justamente isso que o condena.</div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Símbolo:</strong> o violino é a ponte para a humanidade perdida; o momento de quase-redenção que precipita o fim.</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept warn\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">02</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>02</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 10L56 52H8L32 10z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"22\" r=\"2\" fill=\"currentColor\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">Da Compaixão à Sentença</div><div class=\"card-body\">Grete, antes cuidadora, completa o arco de menina a mulher e a juíza: declara que <strong>aquela criatura já não é Gregor e tem de sumir</strong>. Gregor escuta cada palavra — e, sem revolta, lhe dá razão.</div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 8l20 8v13c0 14-9 23-20 27-11-4-20-13-20-27V16z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Para refletir:</strong> a frase de Grete mata Gregor mais que a maçã; o afeto vira repúdio.</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">03</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>03</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M6 38c6-8 12-8 18 0s12 8 18 0 12-8 16 0\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><path d=\"M6 26c6-8 12-8 18 0s12 8 18 0 12-8 16 0\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">A Morte como Alívio</div><div class=\"card-body\">Esvaziado, ferido e faminto, Gregor recolhe-se ao quarto e morre ao amanhecer, ainda pensando na família com ternura. A faxineira acha o corpo seco e o descarta. <strong>A reação dos Samsa não é luto, mas alívio.</strong></div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Leitura:</strong> a morte é a única saída do absurdo; Gregor a aceita — e nisso há uma estranha dignidade.</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide concept\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"top:118px;right:60px;font-size:330px\">04</div><div class=\"topbar\"><span class=\"brandmark\"><span class=\"seal\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M32 16C26 12 16 12 12 14v34c4-2 14-2 20 2 6-4 16-4 20-2V14c-4-2-14-2-20 2z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M32 18v34\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/></svg></span>Minuto<b>Real</b></span><span class=\"count\"><b>04</b><span class=\"sl\">/</span>04</span></div><div class=\"card-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M6 50l16-30 10 16 8-12 18 26z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></div><div class=\"card-title\">O Renascimento dos Vivos</div><div class=\"card-body\">Libertos, os Samsa despedem os hóspedes e saem num passeio de bonde ao campo. Ao sol, os pais notam que <strong>Grete desabrochou numa bela jovem</strong> em idade de casar. A vida segue, indiferente ao morto.</div><div class=\"card-tip\"><span class=\"tipic\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><span><strong>Ironia final:</strong> a obra fecha não no luto, mas no futuro — Kafka nega a Gregor qualquer redenção dos vivos.</span></div><div class=\"dots\"><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"\"></i><i class=\"on\"></i><i class=\"\"></i></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide cta\"><div class=\"ghost\" style=\"bottom:150px;right:40px;font-size:300px\">+</div><div class=\"big\">Gostou?<br><span class=\"lt\">tem mais.</span></div><div class=\"rows\"><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M14 12h36v40H14z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/><path d=\"M14 24h36M14 38h36M24 12v12M40 24v14\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>O livro inteiro em 1 página: cheat sheet + PDF no <strong>acervo</strong> &mdash; link na bio.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"32\" r=\"22\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\"/><path d=\"M27 23l16 9-16 9z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Prefere assistir? Resumo de ~5 min no <strong>YouTube</strong>.</p></div><div class=\"row\"><span class=\"rico\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"><path d=\"M34 8L18 36h12l-4 20 20-30H34l4-18z\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></span><p>Um grande livro destilado por semana. <strong>Siga @minutoreal1701</strong>.</p></div></div><div class=\"save\">